ActOther Than Statutory Authority
PrecisAppointment of the HONOURABLE KARAN M. SHANER, a Judge of the Supreme Court of the Northwest Territories, to be a Justice of Appeal of the Court of Appeal of Alberta, and a Judge ex officio of the Court of King's Bench of Alberta; and a Judge of the Court of Appeal of the Northwest Territories and a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Nunavut during her tenure of office as a Justice of Appeal of the Court of Appeal of Alberta.
